# Repo is intentionally lockfile-less: a committed lockfile makes Cloudflare Pages
# run `npm clean-install` instead of `npm install`. (The ERESOLVE build failure was
# actually an upstream next-on-pages peer conflict, fixed in .npmrc.)
package-lock.json
